      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Medical)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 5</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 18 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 6 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 18</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You cure the target of temporary blindness or deafness (choose one). Once per day, you can use this technique to reduce a target's penalties to attack rolls, saves and skill checks suffered by mangekyou blindness by 2.</p>\n\n\n\n",
